channel.title: @~HELP~@ Only I Can Log Into My Server!
channel.description:
Okay, when you download a server, you can login with the IP 0.0.0.0 and port 5555 :)
I can still log in with that but also I can log in with the IP 192.168.1.2 (not my IP address) :|
Why can't I log in with my IP? :confused:
Why can't others log in with 192.168.1.2? :confused:
:confused:
